---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import redesimg from "../assets/redes.webp";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<Layout title="Redes - Ingenieria IT">
  <section
    class="w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center py-12 lg:py-24"
  >
    <div
      class="container grid items-center gap-6 px-4 md:px-6 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-12"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center space-y-4">
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-5xl">
            Redes confiables para su negocio
          </h2>
          <p
            class="max-w-[600px] text-gray-500 md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed xl:text-xl/relaxed dark:text-gray-400"
          >
            Conecte sus oficinas y proporcione acceso seguro a sus empleados con
            nuestras soluciones de red gestionada. Mantenemos su red segura,
            estable y lista para el futuro.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-2 py-4">
          <li>
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="mr-2 inline-block h-4 w-4"
            >
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            Conexiones seguras con VPN
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="mr-2 inline-block h-4 w-4"
            >
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            Wi-Fi rápido y fiable
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="mr-2 inline-block h-4 w-4"
            >
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            Redes de área amplia (WAN) para sucursales
          </li>
        </div>
        <a
          class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-gray-900 px-8 text-sm font-medium text-gray-50 shadow transition-colors hover:bg-gray-900/90 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-gray-950 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 dark:bg-gray-50 dark:text-gray-900 dark:hover:bg-gray-50/90 dark:focus-visible:ring-gray-300"
          href="#"
          rel="ugc"
        >
          Contactar
        </a>
      </div>
      <Image
        src={redesimg}
        width="650"
        height="350"
        alt="Image"
        class="mx-auto aspect-video overflow-hidden rounded-xl object-cover object-center"
      />
    </div>
    <section class="w-full justify-center flex items-center py-12 md:py-24 lg:py-32 border-t">
      <div class="container px-4 md:px-6">
        <div class="grid gap-10 sm:px-10 md:gap-16 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-gray-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm dark:bg-gray-800">Rendimiento</div>
            <h2 class="lg:leading-tighter text-3xl font-bold tracking-tighter sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl xl:text-[3.4rem] 2xl:text-[3.75rem]">
              Los picos de tráfico deberían ser emocionantes, no aterradores.
            </h2>
            <a
              class="inline-flex h-9 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-gray-900 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-50 shadow transition-colors hover:bg-gray-900/90 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-gray-950 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 dark:bg-gray-50 dark:text-gray-900 dark:hover:bg-gray-50/90 dark:focus-visible:ring-gray-300"
              href="#"
              rel="ugc"
            >
              Empezar
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-start space-y-4">
            <div class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-gray-100 px-3 py-1 text-sm dark:bg-gray-800">Seguridad</div>
            <p class="mx-auto max-w-[700px] text-gray-500 md:text-xl/relaxed dark:text-gray-400">
              Infraestructura totalmente gestionada diseñada para escalar dinámicamente con su tráfico, un borde
              global para garantizar que su sitio sea rápido para cada cliente y las herramientas para monitorear
              cada aspecto de su aplicación.
            </p>
            <a
              class="inline-flex h-9 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-gray-200 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium shadow-sm transition-colors hover:bg-gray-100 hover:text-gray-900 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-gray-950 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-gray-800 dark:bg-gray-950 dark:hover:bg-gray-800 dark:hover:text-gray-50 dark:focus-visible:ring-gray-300"
              href="#"
              rel="ugc"
            >
              Contactar ventas
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>
</Layout>
